WEBVTT

00:00.125 --> 00:04.279
A mother sheep and seven little lambs live in a house.

00:05.301 --> 00:08.945
Dears, I am going to buy some vegetables.

00:09.883 --> 00:13.809
Watch out. There is a bad wolf in the forest.

00:14.785 --> 00:16.875
He is very dangerous.

00:17.833 --> 00:20.117
Don't open the door to the wolf!

00:21.111 --> 00:23.840
Yes, mom. Don't worry!

00:24.941 --> 00:28.641
After a while, a big wolf appears.

00:29.673 --> 00:30.772
Who is it?

00:31.882 --> 00:34.271
Kids, your mommy is home.

00:35.461 --> 00:36.215
Huh?

00:37.337 --> 00:40.718
No! Your voice is so rough!

00:42.229 --> 00:45.216
The wolf goes to eat some eggs.

00:45.883 --> 00:47.501
Soon he comes back.

